<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Devpendent</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Devpendent.styles.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.typekit.net/iuj7zna.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="home-main">
        <img class="home-bg" src="/media/background.jpg" alt="Desk in front of a wall" />
        <div class="home-overlay">
            <header>
                <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-toggleable-sm mb-3">
                    <div class="container-fluid">
                        <a class="navbar-brand" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index"><img class="home-logo" alt="Devpendent Logo" /></a>
                        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target=".navbar-collapse" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
                                aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="21" viewBox="0 0 30 21">
                                    <g transform="translate(-3 -7.5)">
                                        <path d="M4.5,18h27" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" />
                                        <path d="M4.5,9h27" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" />
                                        <path d="M4.5,27h27" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" />
                                    </g>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                        </button>
                        <div class="navbar-collapse collapse d-sm-inline-flex justify-content-end">
                            <ul class="navbar-nav">
                                <li class="nav-item">
                                    <a class="nav-link text-white" asp-area="" asp-controller="Projects" asp-action="Index">Browse</a>
                                </li>
                                <partial name="_HomeLoginPartial" />
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </nav>
            </header>
            <div class="home-text">
                <h1 class="home-title">Hire freelance developers on your own terms</h1>
                <p class="home-desc">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Pellentesque quam est, tempus ut dictum vitae, porta vitae arcu. Nunc quis scelerisque arcu. Proin vitae metus malesuada, semper magna in, faucibus ex. Donec at dui dolor. Duis auctor ultricies nulla, nec sodales metus pulvinar id. Nullam tristique egestas orci, eu pretium libero mollis sit amet. Proin at condimentum neque, quis ultricies metus. Aliquam non commodo magna, eget ullamcorper metus. Pellentesque neque nulla, dignissim sed varius vitae, bibendum id velit.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <main role="main">
            <div class="row">
                <partial name="_NotificationPartial" />
                @RenderBody()
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer border-footer">
        <div class="footer-main">
            <div>
                <h3>Categories</h3>
